---
import ChatLayout from '../layouts/ChatLayout.astro';
import '../styles/prose.css';
---

<ChatLayout title="About" description="A bit about me.">
  <div class="prose">
    <h1>About</h1>

    <p>
      Hi - I'm <strong>Rishabh Anand</strong>, a designer and engineer who enjoys building things that
      are both useful and well-crafted. I care about the details: the spacing, the interaction, the
      words on the screen.
    </p>

    <h2>What I do</h2>
    <p>
      I work at the intersection of design and engineering - writing code that ships, and designing
      systems that scale. My background spans product design, front-end development, and a long
      obsession with typography.
    </p>

    <h2>Currently</h2>
    <p>
      Building products, writing occasionally, and thinking about how software can be more humane.
      You can browse my <a href="/work">selected work</a> or read what I've been thinking about on
      the <a href="/blog">blog</a>.
    </p>

    <h2>Get in touch</h2>
    <p>Always happy to talk - reach out via the <a href="/contact">contact page</a>.</p>
  </div>
</ChatLayout>
